data.description: WOW! This completely remodeled home is waiting on you. Inside this four sided brick home offers 3 BR and 2 BA, new flooring throughout, new light fixtures and faucets, fresh paint, new interior and exterior doors, new kitchen cabinets, new granite kitchen counters, new subway tile backsplash in the kitchen, new farm style kitchen sink, new bathroom vanities, a new roof and so much more! The Kitchen is open to the Den (so you can cook and entertain). Don't forget about your new front porch that would be perfect for sitting and drinking your morning coffee while having a mountain view. You have plenty of privacy with this secluded home that is located in the heart of Lincoln. Call today to schedule your private tour.
